| Static Maps URL: 600×300, zoom 15, red marker | ✅ | |
| Readback: `speechSynthesis`, `utt.lang = detectedLanguage` | ✅ | |
| Submit: POST `/api/analyze` with correct body shape | ✅ | `{ transcript, photoBase64, mimeType, worker, site, lat, lng }` |
| `photoBase64` strips `data:image/jpeg;base64,` prefix | ✅ | `.split(',')[1]` |
| `setState('processing')` during fetch | ✅ | |
| `renderResultPanel`: badge class, all fields, materials pills | ✅ | |
| `#result-urgency-badge` CSS class `urgency-{level}` | ✅ | |
| `#result-materials-row` hidden when empty | ✅ | |
| `#webhook-status` WEBHOOK_LABEL_SUCCESS / FAILURE constants | ✅ | |
| `#usage-counter` → `requests_used/50` | ✅ | |
| `RESTART_COOLDOWN_MS = 2000` on both restart buttons | ✅ | |
| `clearAppState` resets photo/audio/transcript, preserves worker/site/GPS | ✅ | |
| `sanitise`: 2000 chars, strip backticks and backslashes | ✅ | Applied to Whisper output before storing |
| `fetchWithRetry`: 1 retry, 3000 ms delay | ✅ | |
| `escapeHtml` used before any `.innerHTML` write | ✅ | maps_link + material pills |
| No `window.SpeechRecognition` | ✅ | |
| No textarea fallback | ✅ | |

---

## One discrepancy to resolve before writing api/transcribe.js

**`/api/transcribe` transport:**  
This file sends `FormData` with fields `audio` (Blob) and `mimeType` (string).  
CLAUDE.md describes the API as receiving a **raw audio binary body** with `Content-Type` header carrying the MIME type.  
These are incompatible. **Recommendation:** follow this file's FormData contract and write `api/transcribe.js` to match — `multer`/manual `formData` parse on the server side is straightforward in Node.js. Update CLAUDE.md accordingly.

